---
source: tests/help.rs
expression: "help(&[\"skills\", \"install\", \"--help\"])"
---
Install or update the okq-* skills (idempotent)

Usage: okq skills install [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --bundle <DIR>   Bundle directory to query [default: current directory]
      --global         Install into your home dirs (~/.agents, ~/.claude) for all projects
      --from-repo      Fetch the latest skills from GitHub instead of the copy embedded in this binary (the only okq command that uses the network — ADR-0007)
      --json           Emit machine-readable JSON on stdout instead of human-readable text
      --no-color       Disable colored output (also honors NO_COLOR)
      --via-skills-sh  Delegate to skills.sh: run `npx skills add mikevalstar/okq`
      --no-ignore      Ignore all .okqignore files; query the full tree, nothing excluded
  -h, --help           Print help
